      <trans-unit id="about.bio.1" datatype="html">
        <source>Desenvolvedor Full Stack focado em construir produtos digitais completos, eficientes e escaláveis — do banco de dados à interface, sempre alinhando entrega técnica aos objetivos de negócio. Atualmente em transição de júnior para pleno, cursando Tecnólogo em Análise e Desenvolvimento de Sistemas na UniSENAI.</source>
        <target>Full Stack Developer focused on building complete, efficient and scalable digital products — from the database to the interface, always aligning technical delivery with business goals. Currently transitioning from junior to mid-level, pursuing a degree in Systems Analysis and Development at UniSENAI.</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/components/about/about.ts</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">12</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="about.bio.2" datatype="html">
        <source>Construo APIs RESTful com o ecossistema Java, Kotlin e Spring Boot, modelo bancos relacionais (PostgreSQL e MySQL) com foco em performance, e desenvolvo interfaces com Angular e Tailwind CSS — entregando funcionalidades de ponta a ponta.</source>
        <target>I build RESTful APIs with the Java, Kotlin and Spring Boot ecosystem, model relational databases (PostgreSQL and MySQL) with a focus on performance, and develop interfaces with Angular and Tailwind CSS — delivering end-to-end features.</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/components/about/about.ts</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">13</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="about.bio.3" datatype="html">
        <source>Tenho compromisso com qualidade e longevidade de código: aplico SOLID, DRY, KISS, Clean Code, Clean Architecture e DDD no dia a dia, escrevo testes com JUnit, Mockito e Jest, e uso Docker e CI/CD para deploy em nuvem na AWS. Trabalho com Scrum/Kanban e mantenho fluxo organizado mesmo em contexto remoto. Incorporo ferramentas de IA ao fluxo de trabalho para acelerar prototipagem e tarefas repetitivas, sempre revisando e validando cada entrega com o mesmo rigor técnico.</source>
        <target>I care about code quality and longevity: I apply SOLID, DRY, KISS, Clean Code, Clean Architecture and DDD in my day-to-day work, write tests with JUnit, Mockito and Jest, and use Docker and CI/CD for cloud deployment on AWS. I work with Scrum/Kanban and keep an organized workflow even in a remote context. I bring AI tools into my workflow to speed up prototyping and repetitive tasks, always reviewing and validating every delivery with the same technical rigor.</target>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/components/about/about.ts</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">14</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
